    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067350/extras/0e7d35b79dad0947c6fbba6dd7cde13f.poster.avif?t=1752020479\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067350/extras/0e7d35b79dad0947c6fbba6dd7cde13f.webm?t=1752020479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067350/extras/0e7d35b79dad0947c6fbba6dd7cde13f.mp4?t=1752020479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱又帅气的4位角色「美琴」、「稚」、「唯月」、「柚叶」将踏上异世界的旅程，展开拯救被邪恶势力魅影掳走的「薙」的冒险故事。玩家将击败挡在前方的魅影手下，逐步突破8个关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏不仅具备媲美格斗游戏的多样化动作与心理战要素，还加入了通过击败敌人来提升等级、获取点数并学习技能的成长要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升角色等级与操作技巧，成功救出「薙」，并返回原本的世界吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏引擎的进化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这次使用Unreal Engine 5重新打造本作，以流畅的操作与华丽的必杀技，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供更丰富的在线体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >支援合作与对战模式的多人游玩模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本地最多支援4人合作模式与对战模式，也支援在线最多6人合作模式、最多8人对战模式。透过跨平台连线游戏，与全世界的玩家们进行愉快地合作与对战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可游玩敌人角色！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在也可以游玩在《Phantom Breaker: Battle Grounds》世界观中登场的各种敌人角色了！从战力强大的角色到实力欠佳的小卒们都齐聚一堂。可操作的角色总数多达 38 名！在完成剧情模式结局后，这些角色将可在合作模式与对战模式中使用。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067350/extras/d8135e92eb23a673ecb0ec346308f3e4.poster.avif?t=1752020479\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067350/extras/d8135e92eb23a673ecb0ec346308f3e4.webm?t=1752020479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067350/extras/d8135e92eb23a673ecb0ec346308f3e4.mp4?t=1752020479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重製配乐</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以选择由女子摇滚乐队「The Phantom Breakers」编曲的全新乐曲或选择聆听原有的经典版本。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里是日本的首都——东京。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神秘男子——魅影试图取回自身被封印的强大力量，而在暗中活动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他将名为F.A（Fu-mantion Artifact）的武器交给具有特殊能力的年轻人，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并且声称只要打赢战斗就能实现愿望，利用花言巧语诱使他们参加战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为F.A之间的激烈冲突会造成时空扭曲，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >产生出通往另一个世界的裂缝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而那道裂缝最后将能破除他的力量封印。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067350/extras/303eac75f1c985d6e8f4eb88ed556634.poster.avif?t=1752020479\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067350/extras/303eac75f1c985d6e8f4eb88ed556634.webm?t=1752020479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067350/extras/303eac75f1c985d6e8f4eb88ed556634.mp4?t=1752020479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对抗魅影的破邪一族——九纹家长女“稚”，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以及提议一起合作的“美琴”试图阻止这场阴谋，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >却在几乎要成功时被他逃掉了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“稚”的妹妹“薙”在那时遭到了魅影绑架。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立志成为正义使者的女仆“唯月”，以及逃过魅影诱惑的忍者“柚叶”也与她们会合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了救出薙，四名少女开始追踪魅影。</p>",
